## popups.module.js

**Summary:** Declares the `popUps` AngularJS module with a dependency on the `reports` module. Provides popup UI components for reporting publications and managing publication settings (edit, delete, chat, forum access).

**Dependencies:**
- app/app/reports/reports.module.js — depends on the `reports` module

**Tags:** popups, module, angularjs, ui

**Implementation:** app/app/popUps/popups.module.js
